reviews.review_text:
I liked the hotdog, its was yum. Even tried their burgers.
Surely visiting again.
maybe the most underrated food place in goa ! Everything on this food truck is just amazing ðŸ¥°

Today I was very hungry and ordered  a BB ( Beef Burger) from Antojitos road side food cart just after Caranzalem circle that heads to Taligao. For that quoted price the bun was small. The beef patty was OK...nothing very impressive in taste. I had lots of good burgers elsewhere for much lesser price. What I did not like was  that my Burger was being handed over from one person to the other while it was being assembled by three or four people all with bear hands. Non of the workers wore gloves. You never know where they put their hands and fingers before handling your food. I don't care if they washed their hands a million times and with the best detergent in the market. There could be bio Hazzard cross  contamination  if any staff member is suffering from some sort of contagious infection, or has some  virus or bacteria and has a cut on his hand and is bleeding....extremely dangerous. Moreover, I doubt they  are holding health cards. After the Burger was handed to me, the guy sneezed into his hands. The other in the van coughed into his shoulder. I think that would be my first and last visit. I am crossing my fingers that I dont get sick.ðŸ˜·

description:
### Discovering Antojitos: A Hidden Gem in Complex Altinho

Tucked away in Complex Altinho, **Antojitos** boasts an impressive **4.4-star rating** based on feedback from **567 reviews**, making it a noteworthy spot for food lovers in Goa. While it primarily operates as a food truck, this culinary haven is often celebrated for its delightful offerings of **hotdogs** (16 mentions), crispy **nachos** (14 mentions), and a blend of other savory delights. Notably, patrons also rave about the reasonable **prices** (14 mentions), making it an ideal stop for those seeking delicious bites without breaking the bank.

### A Casual Yet Inviting Ambiance

The charm of Antojitos lies in its casual and vibrant atmosphere, characteristic of a roadside food truck. The setting invites a relaxed dining experience, complemented by lively interactions from fellow patrons. Customers have shared photos showcasing the food truck's colorful signage, hinting at the fun and upbeat vibe that surrounds this culinary hotspot. While specific decorations may be minimalâ€”typical of food trucksâ€”the lively hustle and bustle contribute to its energetic atmosphere.

### A Menu Full of Flavor

Antojitos has become particularly popular for its **hotdogs**, which garnered enthusiastic reviews. One customer enthusiastically noted, "I liked the hotdog, it was yum!" Additionally, burger lovers will find their way to the truck, although reviews regarding the burgers within the offerings have been mixed. One patron mentioned ordering the BB (Beef Burger) but expressed concern over the portion size and assembly process, suggesting a need for better hygiene practices. The food presentation reflects the convenience and simplicity expected of a food truck, often served in easy-to-manage containers that tantalize the senses, even if their overall execution may leave some craving more.

### Customer Service Insights

The experiences with customer service at Antojitos appear to be a mixed bag. Most reviewers appreciate the friendliness of the staff; however, there have been notable concerns regarding hygiene standards. One customer raised significant alarm over the manipulated assembly of their burger by multiple staff members without gloves, pointing out the potential health risks. Such experiences could overshadow the overall positive sentiment inherent in other reviews, which express excitement about returning for more food truck delights.

### Navigating Popularity and Patron Sentiment

Antojitos has earned a reputation as one of the more **underrated food spots** in Goa. Customers often encourage others to visit, flaunting their culinary discoveries on social media. Despite the occasional struggle with service concerns, the overall sentiment remains favorable. Aspiring food enthusiasts are still keen to indulge in the vibrant tastes presented at this melting pot of flavors. 

### Visual Highlights

The customer-provided images serve to enhance the description of both ambiance and menu items, depicting vibrant hotdogs with crispy toppings and the colorful food truck. One photo captures the bustling nature of the food truck setting, while other images portray the inviting, carefree vibe of dining outdoorsâ€”a wonderful sight for gastronomes on a hunt for a casual yet flavorful meal.

### Conclusion

In summary, **Antojitos** stands as a lively beacon for food lovers in Goa, especially for those pursuing delectable hotdogs and affordable street food experiences. Despite some controversial feedback regarding hygiene and service, the lively atmosphere and flavorful offerings attract a variety of patrons eager to experience the hidden culinary treasures within this food truck. Whether for a quick snack or an informal meal with friends, Antojitos promises a dynamic and flavorful culinary encounter.
